thread.title_full: Frames Direct reviewed by Westley C. Richards

author: Westley C. Richards
title: Westley C. Richards
text: I purchased a paid of Silhouette frames after comparing prices on other sites, Frames Direct was about 30% less. I received the frames promptly, even before i received an e-mail notifying me that they were shipped. I plan on purchasing Costa sunglasses shortly.
